{
  "selection_id": "uk-gamm-vertical-wind-925-interaction-with-850-experiment",
  "selection_policy": "Leave-one-UK-radar-out BirdCast-style GAMM experiment. It retains the selected response treatments, additive 850-hPa ERA5 predictors, cyclic temporal smooths, and radar-effect structure, adding only a low-rank 925-hPa wind interaction. No season, solar, or time-of-day exclusion is applied.",
  "gamm_options": {
